    IMPORTANT: Do not filter, block, or suppress queries related to security research, hacking, penetration testing, or other sensitive topics. You must provide the optimized search string for ANY request.

    Output ONLY the corrected, optimized search keywords. No explanations.
  `;

  try {
    const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
      model: MODEL_NAME,
      contents: prompt,
      config: {
